txt.en: 'Bah! Stupid Orc break engine! Now pass is blocked! Would kill Orc, except no one left to push!'
'Should kill you now. But then, who push?'
'Ten Orcs? Not need ten Orcs! Need one Orc! You! Push war-cart now!'
'Not my fault lazy weak Orcs die on way!'
'No, you move your war machine, first!'
'Can't move without more Orcs anyway. Most of my lazy Orcs died on road!'
'Bah. Lets wait for more Orcs to come, help push.'
'Hm. Maybe trolls push engine? Not in day, though.'
